1. Moj *dvorišni* pas voli da trči u dvorištu. (My backyard dog likes to run in the yard.)
2. Želim da posadim cveće u *dvorištu*. (I want to plant flowers in the yard.)
3. Njihova kuća ima veliko *dvorište*. (Their house has a large yard.)
4. Molim vas da parkirate automobil u *dvorištu*. (Please park the car in the yard.)
5. Deca se igraju na *dvorištu* ispred škole. (The children are playing on the playground in front of the school.)
6. Danas ću očistiti *dvorište* od lišća. (Today I will clean the yard from the leaves.)
7. U *dvorištu* se nalazi stari hrast. (There is an old oak tree in the yard.)
8. Gledam kroz prozor i vidim komšijinu mačku kako se šeta po *dvorištu*. (I am looking out the window and I see the neighbor's cat walking around in the yard.)
9. Našao sam ključ u *dvorištu*. (I found a key in the yard.)
10. Dok sam se vraćao kući, video sam grupu golubova u *dvorištu*. (As I was coming back home, I saw a group of pigeons in the yard.)